Package: org.lappsgrid.metadata

[Groovy] Class ServiceMetadataBuilder

    • org.lappsgrid.metadata.ServiceMetadataBuilder

    • Implements the Builder pattern for generating ServiceMetadata. 

               ServiceMetadata md = new ServiceMetadataBuilder()
                                  .version("2.0.0")
                                  .vendor("http://example.com")
                                  .produces("http://vocab.lappsgrid.org/Token")
                                  .build();
      The ServiceMetadataBuilder.toString method can be used to obtain the JSON representation rather than the ServiceMetadata object itself.
      Authors:
      Keith Suderman
